description: The FBI announced on Monday it had successfully gained access to the phone used by Thomas Matthew Crooks, the suspected shooter in the attempted assassination of former President Donald Trump.
title: FBI Gains Access to Suspected Trump Shooter’s Password Locked Phone

description: An underground site is selling videos and photos of real people to bypass selfie checks for online services. In essence, these individuals have been turned into stock models for services specifically designed for fraud.
title: Inside the Face Fraud Factory
